138
00:11:18.344 --> 00:11:21.931 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
悟さ… 覚えてる？

139
00:11:22.306 --> 00:11:23.391 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
（悟）何？

140
00:11:24.892 --> 00:11:27.728 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:82.33% 
あんたが
小学５年だったかん時―

141
00:11:27.853 --> 00:11:29.730 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
近所で起きた事件

142
00:11:31.315 --> 00:11:32.441 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
いや…

143
00:11:32.942 --> 00:11:35.528 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
（佐知子）私らも必死だったのさ

144
00:11:35.611 --> 00:11:41.325 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:82.33% 
子どもらから事件の記憶
少しでも 取り除こうとしたんだ

145
00:11:43.494 --> 00:11:46.789 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
悟 危ないとこだったんだよ

146
00:11:58.092 --> 00:12:00.094 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
（悟）小学５年生の時―

147
00:12:00.219 --> 00:12:02.638 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
連続誘拐殺人事件が起こったんだ

148
00:12:02.763 --> 00:12:08.769 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
♪～

149
00:12:16.861 --> 00:12:19.196 position:50.00%,middle align:start size:80.00% line:10.00% 
３人いた
被害者のうち―

150
00:12:19.280 --> 00:12:21.365 position:50.00%,middle align:start size:80.00% line:10.00% 
２人は同じクラス

151
00:12:22.366 --> 00:12:24.910 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
そして 逮捕された犯人も―

152
00:12:24.994 --> 00:12:27.037 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
よく知っている人だった…

153
00:12:27.455 --> 00:12:28.539 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
（ユウキ）悟君

154
00:12:28.914 --> 00:12:31.750 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:82.33% 
（ユウキ）クラスの人気者のこと
当ててみようか？

155
00:12:32.084 --> 00:12:33.043 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
（悟）え？

156
00:12:33.752 --> 00:12:36.505 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
明るくて スポーツが得意

157
00:12:37.089 --> 00:12:41.844 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:82.33% 
ふざけることもあるけど
はっきり ものを言って―

158
00:12:42.344 --> 00:12:45.556 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:82.33% 
何か１つの物事に対して
真面目なやつ

159
00:12:47.516 --> 00:12:51.145 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:82.33% 
友達が欲しいなら
マネしてみたら どうかな？

160
00:12:51.937 --> 00:12:55.566 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
恥ずかしがらずに 勇気を持って

161
00:12:56.775 --> 00:12:58.152 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
（悟）勇気…

162
00:12:58.861 --> 00:12:59.862 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
（悟）よく―

163
00:12:59.945 --> 00:13:02.907 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:82.33% 
“勇気”という ことばを
連発するこの人を―

164
00:13:03.032 --> 00:13:03.949 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
僕は―

165
00:13:04.283 --> 00:13:06.327 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
“ユウキさん”と呼んでいた

166
00:13:06.619 --> 00:13:07.620 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
ユウキさんは 今―

167
00:13:08.579 --> 00:13:11.832 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:82.33% 
死刑囚として
刑務所に収監されている

168
00:13:19.590 --> 00:13:22.927 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
これ 本部から見舞金

169
00:13:23.052 --> 00:13:25.095 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
（悟）あっ すいません

170
00:13:25.346 --> 00:13:26.847 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
ところで 悟君

171
00:13:26.972 --> 00:13:30.392 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:82.33% 
社員になるって話
忘れないでいてくれよ

172
00:13:31.143 --> 00:13:35.189 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:82.33% 
あっ マンガに見切りつけてからで
構わないけどね

173
00:13:35.898 --> 00:13:38.108 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:82.33% 
（悟）お気遣い
ありがとうございます

174
00:13:38.234 --> 00:13:40.903 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:82.33% 
じゃ あしたから
（悟）はい

175
00:13:44.782 --> 00:13:46.992 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
（悟）さすがに 買いすぎじゃね？

176
00:13:47.117 --> 00:13:48.994 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
（佐知子）誰か呼べばいいべさ

177
00:13:49.119 --> 00:13:51.247 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
友達とか 彼女とか

178
00:13:51.372 --> 00:13:54.458 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
（悟）いねえよ マンガ一筋だよ

179
00:13:55.251 --> 00:13:57.628 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:82.33% 
（母親）走るから
こうなるんでしょう

180
00:13:57.753 --> 00:14:00.089 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:82.33% 
泣かない！
自分でやったんだから

181
00:14:03.884 --> 00:14:04.718 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
（愛梨）藤沼さん

182
00:14:10.391 --> 00:14:12.017 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
いるべさ

183
00:14:12.142 --> 00:14:13.435 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
（悟）誰が

184
00:14:13.936 --> 00:14:15.604 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
（愛梨）忘れ物 預かってるよ

185
00:14:17.064 --> 00:14:19.733 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:82.33% 
（愛梨）うわっ
（佐知子）ああ 大丈夫かい？

186
00:14:21.777 --> 00:14:22.778 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
（愛梨）はい

187
00:14:25.823 --> 00:14:28.117 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
誰か呼べばいいべさ

188
00:14:28.242 --> 00:14:30.077 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
友達とか 彼女とか

189
00:14:30.202 --> 00:14:32.496 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:82.33% 
（悟）こんなタイミングで
リバイバル？

190
00:14:32.621 --> 00:14:35.249 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
何だ… 何が起きる？

191
00:14:36.292 --> 00:14:37.585 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
どうして走るの？

192
00:14:38.085 --> 00:14:41.005 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
母さん 周りを見てくれないか？

193
00:14:41.255 --> 00:14:43.465 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
ちょっと 変な感じがするんだ

194
00:14:43.591 --> 00:14:44.842 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
え？

195
00:14:45.968 --> 00:14:47.720 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
そういや あんた…

196
00:14:47.845 --> 00:14:50.848 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
昔も同じこと言った時 あったね

197
00:14:51.223 --> 00:14:53.893 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
あん時は ボヤ騒ぎ…

198
00:15:02.067 --> 00:15:03.277 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
（愛梨）藤沼さん

199
00:15:06.780 --> 00:15:08.657 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
忘れ物 預かってるよ

200
00:15:09.116 --> 00:15:10.743 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
（悟）片桐君 走るな 危ない！

201
00:15:10.826 --> 00:15:11.744 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
えっ？

202
00:15:32.765 --> 00:15:35.434 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
（子どもたちの歓声）

203
00:15:35.517 --> 00:15:37.019 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
わあ

204
00:15:37.311 --> 00:15:43.317 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
♪～

205
00:16:05.965 --> 00:16:07.383 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
（愛梨）藤沼さん

206
00:16:09.176 --> 00:16:12.972 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:82.33% 
この本 店長から預かってたのに
渡し忘れちゃった

207
00:16:14.682 --> 00:16:15.975 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
あちらは？

208
00:16:17.559 --> 00:16:18.769 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
おふくろ

209
00:16:19.311 --> 00:16:21.355 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
ええっ！ ええっ…

210
00:16:21.480 --> 00:16:23.941 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
お姉さんかと思ったよ

211
00:16:24.817 --> 00:16:26.819 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
初めまして 片桐愛梨です

212
00:16:26.944 --> 00:16:30.364 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:82.33% 
（佐知子）あっ どうも
藤沼佐知子です

213
00:16:30.489 --> 00:16:32.199 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
ねえ 愛梨さん

214
00:16:32.324 --> 00:16:35.494 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:82.33% 
これから カレー作るけど
食べに来ないかい？

215
00:16:35.619 --> 00:16:37.413 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
はいっ 伺います！

216
00:16:37.538 --> 00:16:39.123 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:82.33% 
（悟）ええっ？
（佐知子）したら 行こうか

217
00:16:39.248 --> 00:16:42.126 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
はい 喜んで 行きます

218
00:16:44.712 --> 00:16:46.964 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
（佐知子）ああ やっぱな…

219
00:16:47.047 --> 00:16:49.049 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:82.33% 
彼女にしちゃ
若すぎると思ったけど―

220
00:16:49.174 --> 00:16:52.136 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
違うんだ… 残念…

221
00:16:52.219 --> 00:16:55.931 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:82.33% 
悟さんは 何ていうか…
尊敬できる お友達です

222
00:16:59.643 --> 00:17:00.853 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
辛かったかい？

223
00:17:02.938 --> 00:17:04.231 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
うめえよ

224
00:17:06.692 --> 00:17:09.945 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
（愛梨）うん… やっぱ おいしい！

225
00:17:10.029 --> 00:17:12.364 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:82.33% 
ホントに
送らせんくて 大丈夫かい？

226
00:17:12.489 --> 00:17:14.116 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
（愛梨）はい 原付きですから

227
00:17:14.199 --> 00:17:15.868 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
それじゃ ごちそうさまでした

228
00:17:19.413 --> 00:17:20.372 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
じゃあ

229
00:17:28.088 --> 00:17:29.173 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
（悟）あのさ…

230
00:17:29.298 --> 00:17:32.509 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:82.33% 
嫁 探してるみたいな
あさましい目で見るなよ

231
00:17:32.634 --> 00:17:34.970 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
ただのバイト仲間なんだから

232
00:17:35.220 --> 00:17:39.016 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:82.33% 
（佐知子）あんたも鈍いねえ
あれは脈ありだべ

233
00:17:39.141 --> 00:17:41.602 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
（悟）そんなんじゃないって

234
00:17:45.230 --> 00:17:49.735 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:82.33% 
そういえば 昼間…
駐車場で何か気が付いた？

235
00:17:51.945 --> 00:17:53.781 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
ああ あれ…

236
00:17:55.491 --> 00:17:58.243 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
誘拐事件が 未遂に終わったよ

237
00:17:58.327 --> 00:17:59.286 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
えっ！？

238
00:18:01.038 --> 00:18:02.831 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
冗談に決まってるべさ

239
00:18:19.515 --> 00:18:26.480 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
（携帯電話の振動音）

240
00:18:34.530 --> 00:18:36.031 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
（澤田(さわだ)）はい…

241
00:18:36.156 --> 00:18:42.162 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
♪～

242
00:18:48.627 --> 00:18:50.379 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
（佐知子）あの男の目…

243
00:18:50.796 --> 00:18:52.589 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
私 知ってる…

244
00:18:55.175 --> 00:18:58.053 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
あの様子は かなり手慣れてる

245
00:18:59.263 --> 00:19:01.974 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
何度も犯行を重ねてるに違いない

246
00:19:05.602 --> 00:19:08.188 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
18年前の誘拐事件…

247
00:19:09.022 --> 00:19:11.150 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
まだ終わってなかった

248
00:19:19.533 --> 00:19:20.742 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
（佐知子）はっ うっ

249
00:19:23.579 --> 00:19:26.665 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
くっ… くっ… はっ…

250
00:19:30.419 --> 00:19:33.046 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
あっ… ハァ…

251
00:19:35.299 --> 00:19:36.717 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
はあ…

252
00:19:38.677 --> 00:19:40.220 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
（佐知子）悟に…

253
00:19:41.597 --> 00:19:43.432 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
伝えなきゃ…

254
00:19:45.058 --> 00:19:47.144 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
ごめんねって…

255
00:19:47.269 --> 00:19:49.062 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
う… ハァ…

256
00:19:50.314 --> 00:19:51.315 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
あ…

257
00:19:52.608 --> 00:19:53.984 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
あ… あ…

258
00:19:54.610 --> 00:19:56.612 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
ああっ… はっ…

259
00:20:07.581 --> 00:20:10.125 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:82.33% 
（悟）あのスーパーで
誘拐事件が未遂に終わったと―

260
00:20:10.250 --> 00:20:11.919 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
おふくろは言っていた

261
00:20:13.128 --> 00:20:17.424 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:82.33% 
“冗談に決まってるべさ”
なんて ごまかしていたけど―

262
00:20:17.549 --> 00:20:22.054 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:82.33% 
おふくろが あれを言う時は
いつも 本当のことを言っている

263
00:20:22.971 --> 00:20:24.848 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
リバイバルしたあと―

264
00:20:24.973 --> 00:20:27.684 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:82.33% 
どうして誘拐が
未遂に終わったんだ？

265
00:20:28.185 --> 00:20:30.896 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:82.33% 
詳しいことを
おふくろに聞いてみないと…

266
00:20:32.105 --> 00:20:35.317 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:82.33% 
（悟）母さん だから
鍵ぐらい閉めろって…

267
00:20:41.949 --> 00:20:43.116 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
おい…

268
00:20:44.993 --> 00:20:46.286 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
うそだろ…

269
00:20:49.539 --> 00:20:51.166 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
返事しろよ

270
00:20:55.212 --> 00:20:56.797 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
やめろって

271
00:21:00.926 --> 00:21:04.054 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
おいっ 起きろよ！

272
00:21:06.515 --> 00:21:10.269 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:82.33% 
言えよ！
“冗談に決まってるべさ”って！

273
00:21:13.522 --> 00:21:17.192 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:82.33% 
上野までは
電車１本で行けんだよ！

274
00:21:19.820 --> 00:21:21.613 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
母さん！

275
00:21:29.162 --> 00:21:31.540 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
ああああっ！

276
00:21:31.623 --> 00:21:37.629 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
♪～

277
00:21:54.187 --> 00:21:55.230 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
（物音）

278
00:21:55.314 --> 00:22:01.320 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
♪～

279
00:22:10.329 --> 00:22:12.247 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
（大家）藤沼さん どうしたの？

